ate rape drugs in a variety of beverages through color change  the problem   in  women will be sexually assaulted in her lifetime this unthinkable problem has reached epidemic levels on college campuses and something must be done about it power must be handed back to women in what is a devastatingly powerless situation      the toolour tech the only perfect solution to drug induced sexual assault is ending it altogether as we all work toward that ideal undercover colors’ technology provides wearable protection at your fingertips simply dip your finger into a verified beverage and within seconds the presence of prevalent date rape drugs will be identified in color change     why us four engineering students walk into a bar…perhaps that’s not exactly how it went… but at the heart of founding undercover colors was a conviction that we could take the power we had as engineers to create something that gave power to others  want to join us   meet steve meet tyler     whos talking it is the newest fashion accessory that may really truly have the power to change livesabc news     be part of it let us keep you in the know on the launchshare your story with us email address sign up thank you    undercover colors inc  north carolina biotech center jump to navigation we make connections that create biotech jobs ncbiotech company directory a comprehensive listing of north carolinas life science industry  new search   undercover colors inc httpwwwundercovercolorscom undercover colors develops a nail polish that changes color in the presence of date rape drugs a product developed to prevent drug facilitated sexual assault   location  main campus drive suite raleigh nc phone  county wakeregion triangle company classification company type support or related company company sector health and beauty productscompany activities support and related funding business services job services news  events about us biotech in nc   become a sponsor  sponsor login questions about the ncbiotech co